  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until charred, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rest-meat and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the green curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the coconut milk, fish sauce, brown sugar, salt, and pepper.",
    "Bring to a simmer, then reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired.",
    "Let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
